title: Show Mission Pass
description: Acquire exclusive Costumes each month with the Premium Mission Pass.

title: Colorful Pass
description: A COLORFUL+ subscription will give you Crystals each day.

title: VIRTUAL SINGERS in other SEKAI?
description: Miku and the other VIRTUAL SINGERS appear differently in each SEKAI, where they help each character find their true feelings.

title: How are SEKAI created?
description: SEKAI are born from someone's true feelings.

title: Untitled?
description: Untitled songs are linked to their SEKAI. They are silent songs with neither melody nor lyrics.

title: Practice Scores - How to Obtain & Use ①
description: Level up your Characters in Practice to get higher scores in shows.

title: Music Cards - How to Obtain & Use
description: Go to the Music Shop to get new songs to play in shows.

title: Music Cards - How to Obtain & Use
description: You can trade Music Cards for new songs. The best way to get these is by viewing stories.

title: Miracle Gems - How to Obtain & Use
description: Upgrade your 3★ and 4★ Characters to get higher scores in shows.

title: Costume Materials - How to Obtain & Use
description: Visit the Costume Shop in the Shopping Mall to get new Costumes.

title: You can use between 0 and 5 Bonus Energy.
description: Use more Bonus Energy to increase the amount of Event Points and other rewards you'll earn.

title: You can use between 0 and 5 Bonus Energy.
description: Bonus Energy restores at a rate of 1 every 30 minutes.

title: Game settings can be changed from the Options screen.
description: Adjust the note speed to what's best for you from the Options menu.

title: Check a character's Profile to see their Info.
description: You can view each character's Profile in the Character Archive.

title: Miku Display in Deck
description: You can select which Miku appears in 3D Music Videos from the Costumes menu.

title: Obtaining Avatar Costumes
description: Visit the Virtual Shop to get Costumes, Accessories and other customization options for your Virtual Avatar.

title: Obtaining Virtual Coins
description: You can obtain Virtual Coins from the Wish Piece Exchange.

title: Virtual Show Rewards
description: Special Virtual Shows are held on characters' birthdays and anniversaries.

title: Virtual Show Rewards
description:
Earn Crystals by viewing a
 Virtual Show for the first time.

title: Changing Costumes
description: Change which Costume a character will wear in 3D music videos from the Costumes menu.

title: Skill Activation in Solo Shows
description: In Solo Shows, each Character's Skill is activated once, except for the Leader's, which activates twice.

title: Skill Activation in Co-op Shows ①
description: In Co-op Shows, the best-performing player's Leader's Skill activates last.

title: Fan Pts - Acquisition & Use
description: Items used in a Virtual Show will earn you Wish Pieces after the Virtual Show is over.

title: MVP and SUPERSTAR
description: Players who perform well in Co-op Shows will be crowned a SUPERSTAR.

title: Being ON FIRE in a Co-op Show
description: If you achieve a long enough combo during a Co-op Show, you will be "On Fire", and every player's score will gain a bonus.

title: View Card Episodes to Boost Stats
description: Many Characters have special Side Stories.

title: Playing Challenge Shows
description: When a character's Challenge Show Level increases, you'll earn Crystals and Character Rank EXP.

title: Playing Challenge Shows
description: Surpass certain high scores in a Challenge Show to earn Crystals.

title: Decorations - Basic Effects
description: Level up your Decorations to get higher scores in shows.

title: Decorations - Basic Effects
description:
Once you own a Decoration, its
 effect will be applied automatically.

title: Unlock Costume Patterns by Getting 4★ Characters.
description: If you get a 4★ Character that comes with a Costume, you'll also be able to make it for other characters to wear.

title: Wishes - Acquisition & Use
description: You can raise a Character's Mastery Rank using Wish Pieces.

title: Wishes - Acquisition & Use
description: Trade Characters in the Green Room for Wish Pieces and Wish Jewels.

title: Wishes - Acquisition & Use
description: Get Wish Pieces by trading 2★, 3★, Birthday or Anniversary Characters in the Green Room.

title: Virtual Show Avatar Appearance
description: You can customize the way your Avatar appears in the Virtual Show Lobby.

title: Increasing Character Rank
description:
You can earn special rewards by
 increasing the Character Rank of your members.

title: Increasing Character Rank
description: Increasing Character Ranks will earn you special Titles and Stamps.

title: Increasing Character Rank
description:
Earn Character Rank EXP by completing
 Challenge Shows and character missions.

title: Earning Titles
description: Earn Titles by clearing various Missions.

title: Earning Titles
description: Titles that increase Talent do not need to be displayed on your profile to have effect.

title: Show Mission Points Reset
description: Show Missions reset at 12:00 a.m. (PT) on the 1st of each month.

title: View Area Bonus Details from the Items Menu
description: You can check the total effect of your Decorations from the Items menu.

title: Decorations - Leveling & Advantages
description: Obtain Magical Seeds by playing shows and use them to level up Decorations.

title: Unlocking Challenge Show Slots
description: The number of slots available for a character's Challenge Shows is determined by their Character Rank.

title: Increase Mastery Rank to Boost Stats
description: Increase a Character's Mastery Rank to earn more Event Points and Tokens during events.

title: Increase Mastery Rank to Boost Stats
description: Increase the Mastery Rank of a 4★ Character that comes with a Costume to unlock that Costume's color variants.

title: Purchasing Song Covers
description:
Some songs have cover versions sung
 by other characters.

title: Purchasing Song Covers
description: You can get Covers of songs from the Cover Shop section of the Music Shop.

title: Purchasing Song Covers
description:
Increase Character Rank to obtain Cover Cards
 which can be traded in at the Cover Shop.

title: Title Display
description: Some Titles vary in appearance depending on rank and other factors.

title: Co-op Show Rewards (1)
description: You can earn more rewards by playing Co-op Shows.

title: Obtaining Stamps
description: Visit the Stamp Shop in the Shopping Mall to get new Stamps.

title: Obtaining Stamp Vouchers
description: The best way to obtain Stamp Vouchers is through Event Exchanges.

title: Virtual Show - Lobby (1)
description:
You can interact with other players
 in the Virtual Show Lobby.

title: Virtual Show - Lobby (2)
description:
Purchase Avatar Costumes, Accessories, and other
 items from the Virtual Shop in the Lobby.

title: Ver. Select
description: Switch song versions before starting a Show by tapping Ver. Select.

title: Assigning Favorite Stamps
description: You can add Stamps to your Favorites from the Stamps menu.

title: Increasing Your Score (1)
description: Your score in a show is determined by your Characters' Talent, your Combos and the number of Perfects you earn.

title: Increasing Your Score (2)
description: Higher combos earn you bigger score boosts.

title: Obtaining Practice Scores
description:
Practice Scores that are used to level up
 your characters, are mainly obtained by completing shows.

title: Music Video Viewer
description: From the Music Video Viewer, you can view 3D, 2D and original music videos.

title: Unlocking New Functions ①
description:
Reach Player Rank 5 to unlock
 the Challenge Show game mode.

title: Unlocking New Functions ③
description:
Reach Player Rank 30 to
 unlock the Skill Up function.

title: Auto-Play
description: You can use Auto-Play to clear Solo Shows for you.

title: Auto-Play
description: Auto-Play can be used up to 10 times per day.

title: Event Story
description: You can view all past stories from the Story menu.

title: Event Story
description: Viewing the final episode of a past Event Story unlocks its After Show.

title: Challenge Shows - EX Levels
description: When a character's Challenge Show Level reaches 100, it will switch to EX Levels.

title: Challenge Shows - EX Levels
description: When a character's Challenge Show Level reaches EX Levels, you will earn Crystals when you level up.

title: Friends
description: You can send a Friend Request to another player from their Profile.

title: Purchasing Song Covers
description:
Cover Cards can be traded in
 at the Cover Card Exchange.

title: Hairstyle
description: Reach Mastery Rank 2 with a Limited Time Character to unlock a special Hairstyle.

title: Hairstyle
description: You can set characters' Hairstyles from the Costume menu.

title: Challenge Stamp
description: Get a stamp each time you Clear a Challenge Show.

title: Challenge Stamp
description: Select a special item as a reward from the Challenge Show Day 7's Challenge Stamp.

title: Dress-up Mode
description: Switch on Dress-up Mode at the Costume Shop to try on Costumes and color variants you haven't obtained yet.

title: Profile
description: Go to the Custom Profile menu to design your own personal Profile.

title: Birthday Character
description: Birthday Characters are special Characters with the Birthday rarity.

title: Character Exchange
description: Trade for previously featured General Characters at the Character Exchange.

title: Event Bonus
description: Increasing Mastery Rank will also earn Event Bonuses.

title: Trust Rank
description: Increase the Trust Rank between certain Characters to earn special Titles.

title: Trust Rank
description: Playing shows earns Trust Rank EXP between the Leader and the other four characters in your group.

title: Friends
description: You can invite friends who are online to a Private Room for Co-op Shows or Virtual Shows.

title: Auto-Play
description: You can set Auto-Play to automatically restore your Bonus Energy in order to continue playing.

title: Ranked Match
description: In Ranked Matches, players will compete each season against one another in 1 vs 1 Shows.

title: Ranked Match
description: To unlock Ranked Matches, you need to reach Player Rank 20 and Full Combo at least 5 songs on Expert or Master difficulty.

title: Wishes - Acquisition & Use
description: Wish Jewels can be exchanged for Wish Pieces at the Wish Piece & Wish Jewel Exchange.

title: Character Archive
description: Earn more Character Rank EXP by clearing Character Missions.

title: Playlists
description: Go to Playlists to make lists of all your favorite songs.

title: ライブPの獲得方法
description: Earn up to three Daily Bonuses a day when clearing Co-op Shows or Cheerful Shows.

title: ライブPの獲得方法
description: Clearing every Bonus Mission during an event will earn you 500 Show Points.

title: ディスクショップ
description: Purchase recordings of past Virtual Shows at the Disc Shop in the Lobby.

title: シアター
description: Recordings purchased at the Disc Shop can be viewed at the Theater in the Lobby.

title: Favorite Stories
description: You can select Favorite Stories to display on your Profile along with your comments.

title: Bookmark
description: When viewing a story, you can bookmark your spot and continue viewing from there later at any time.

title: 記憶のカケラ
description: Touch the Memory Fragment to look into the past and view Area Conversations from the previous school year.

title: 難易度APPEND
description: Append difficulty is a mode that requires three or more fingers to play.

title: ノーツ種類
description: Adjust the note designs and sound effects from the Options menu.

description: Reach Mastery Rank 2 with a Group Event Exclusive Character to unlock a 3DMV Alternate Cut.

title: ライブでライフが0になったとき
description: Even if your Life drops to zero during the rhythm game, you can play the show to the end.

title: CM機能
description: You can earn rewards every day by watching in-game ads.
